Package: pomdp
Title: Infrastructure for Partially Observable Markov Decision Processes
    (POMDP)
Version: 1.2.3-1
Date: 2024-xx-xx
Authors@R: c(
    person("Michael", "Hahsler", , "mhahsler@lyle.smu.edu", role = c("aut", "cph", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2716-1405")),
    person("Hossein", "Kamalzadeh", role = "ctb")
  )
Description: Provides the infrastructure to define and analyze the
    solutions of Partially Observable Markov Decision Process (POMDP)
    models. Interfaces for various exact and approximate solution
    algorithms are available including value iteration, point-based value
    iteration and SARSOP. Smallwood and Sondik (1973)
    <doi:10.1287/opre.21.5.1071>.
License: GPL (>=3)
URL: https://github.com/mhahsler/pomdp
